				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Research into the Cloudflare Workers REST API for programmatic Worker management from a Pharo/Smalltalk HTTP client (no Wrangler CLI). Covers script CRUD, routes, workers.dev subdomain, KV storage, D1 database, and webhook-forwarding patterns.\n\nBase URL: `https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4`\n\nResearch date: 2026-04-16"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:08:28.039044-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:08:28.039044-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "HWpTxN/pQcyjCfyTix1r6g=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "## Authentication\n\nAll endpoints require a Bearer token header:\n`Authorization: Bearer <CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN>`\n\nCreate tokens at the Cloudflare dashboard (Profile > API Tokens). Tokens use a `cfut_` prefix format. Required permissions:\n- **Workers Scripts: Edit** (includes read/list) for script management\n- **Workers KV Storage: Edit** for KV namespace operations\n- **D1: Edit** for D1 database operations\n- **Workers Routes: Edit** for zone-level route management"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
