				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "### 1.1 Upload/Update a Worker Script (the key endpoint)\n\n`PUT /accounts/{account_id}/workers/scripts/{script_name}`\n`Content-Type: multipart/form-data`\n\nThis is the primary deployment endpoint. It accepts a **multipart form** with two parts:\n1. **`metadata`** -- JSON string with script configuration (replaces `wrangler.toml`)\n2. **Script file(s)** -- the JavaScript module(s), with the entry point matching `main_module`\n\nOptional query parameter: `bindings_inherit=strict` fails if unresolvable `inherit` bindings exist.\n\n**Response** returns the script metadata: `id`, `etag`, `handlers`, `compatibility_date`, `created_on`, `modified_on`, `usage_model`, `has_modules`, `placement`, `observability`, `tags`, `startup_time_ms`."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:08:51.543708-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-16T22:08:51.543708-04:00"
					}
