					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "## 2. Workers Routes (Zone-level)\n\nRoutes bind a Worker to a URL pattern on a **custom domain** (zone). This is an alternative to workers.dev when you want `https://yourdomain.com/webhooks/*` style URLs."
			},
