				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "### Create Route request body\n```\n{ \"pattern\": \"example.com/webhooks/*\", \"script\": \"my-webhook-worker\" }\n```\n\nResponse includes the route `id`, `pattern`, and `script` name. The `id` is needed for deletion.\n\n**Pattern syntax:** `example.com/*` matches all paths. `example.com/hooks/*` matches a subpath. Wildcards only at the end."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
