				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "rOI2MlvSR6OEC3a7rctzog=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "## 3. Workers.dev Subdomain\n\nEvery Cloudflare account gets a `*.workers.dev` subdomain. Each Worker deployed gets a **public URL automatically** -- no DNS or custom domain needed.\n\n### URL Format\n`https://{script_name}.{account_subdomain}.workers.dev`\n\nExample: `https://my-webhook.dweinstein.workers.dev`\n\n### Key behavior\n- All Workers are assigned a workers.dev route **by default** when created\n- No extra API call needed for a newly uploaded script to be reachable\n- Can be disabled per-script via the subdomain API\n- If disabled in dashboard but not in wrangler config, re-deploy re-enables it"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "elementSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
