				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "### Create namespace\nRequest: `{ \"title\": \"webhook-events\" }`\nResponse: `{ \"result\": { \"id\": \"0f2ac74b498b48028cb68387c421e279\", \"title\": \"webhook-events\", \"supports_url_encoding\": true } }`\nThe `id` is the `namespace_id` used in bindings and all subsequent KV calls.\n\n### Write key-value\nBody: raw value (string/binary). Query params: `expiration` (unix timestamp) or `expiration_ttl` (seconds, min 60). If both set, `expiration_ttl` wins. Key name max: 512 bytes, use percent-encoding for special characters.\n\n### Read value\nReturns raw value content. Expiration timestamp in `expiration` response header if set.\n\n### List keys\nQuery params: `prefix` (filter by name prefix), `limit`, `cursor` (pagination). Returns array of `{ name, expiration, metadata }` objects plus `result_info` with `cursor` for next page."
			},
