				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "### Create D1 database\nRequest: `{ \"name\": \"webhook-store\", \"primary_location_hint\": \"enam\" }`\nLocation hints: `wnam`, `enam`, `weur`, `eeur`, `apac`, `oc`. Optional `jurisdiction`: `eu` or `fedramp`.\nResponse includes `uuid` (the `database_id` / binding `id`), `name`, `created_at`, `num_tables`, `file_size`.\n\n### Query D1 database\nSingle: `{ \"sql\": \"SELECT * FROM events WHERE source = ?\", \"params\": [\"github\"] }`\nBatch: `{ \"batch\": [ { \"sql\": \"CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS events (...)\" }, { \"sql\": \"INSERT ...\", \"params\": [...] } ] }`\nResponse: array of `{ success, results: [...rows], meta: { duration, rows_read, rows_written, served_by_region } }`"
			},
