					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "## 6. Webhook Worker Script Examples\n\nAll scripts use ES Module format (`export default { async fetch(request, env, ctx) { ... } }`). The `env` parameter provides access to bindings. The `ctx` parameter offers `waitUntil()` for background work after response."
			},
